race.comment: TERESITA (1) charged out of the boxes with a fast early split and led throughout to score when a 0.8 lengths winner (29.61) over 520m at Wentworth Park. The form from her last run stacks up well. Ideally placed to take this out. DRINK TINS (2) scored (25.19) last time out at Q Lakeside adding to an already respectable career. Form at the trip sound including eight wins. The form out of his last race has been franked. One of main contenders. KISSES FOR GRAN (3) was well supported last time but could only manage second (25.62), beaten 5.5 lengths. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Ready to find winning form. PARTY MODE (8) is a last-start placegetter at this track and distance - solid claims again.
